data.meta_description: Eventbrite - Flash presents Nü Androids presents SünDown: Pretty Girl (DJ Set) - Saturday, September 14, 2024 at Flash, Washington, DC. Find event and ticket information.
data.text: Producer, vocalist, and DJ, Pretty Girl makes her Nü Androids debut on the Flash rooftop on Saturday, September 14th. Her feel good sound that brings emotion to the club with her warm-blooded productions and captivating live sets will make this one you won’t want to miss. Be there as the Nü Fam gets a +1 as Pretty Girl joins the familia!
